I did it! Freedom... I'm like a bird
who flew from her cage!

Father and Brother treat me like I'm
a child. Put a spear in my hands, and
I'll put the boys to shame!

There was some fruit left over from
breakfast, so I took some! Let's put
it in water with honey and drink it!

Hey! What're you doing? Let me help!
C'mon, $Nu!

I can take care of myself. Whenever
I'm in the castle, though, a bunch of
guards always follow me around...

How nice to meet you! I'm Tana,
from Frelia. I've come to meet you
on behalf of $Nf.

I bet you didn't expect that!
...I didn't even expect it!

Focus, Tana! Focus! Ephraim and
Eirika are surely doing their best
right now. I have to do the same!
What? Ugh... C'mon!

I'm going to get even stronger than
my brother while he's not looking!

Nice to meet you. I'm Tana, princess
of Frelia—not that noble status means
anything... Let's be friends!

Let me ask you something... If I'm the
princess of Frelia, is it so wrong for
me to play like a normal girl?$k$p"Remember your duty as royalty,"
says my brother. Pompous! How can
I learn anything behind castle walls?$k$pI love Frelia... The smell of the forest,
the wind off the sea... And I love the
people that live there!$k$pEirika understands... We may not
get to see each other often, but
she's my best friend...$k$pIf my brother had his way, he would
likely bully Eirika, Ephraim, and the
others, but I'll defend them!$k$pOh! Does that count as my duty as
royalty? If so, being a princess is all
right then.$k$pI'll protect the people of Frelia!
Yeah... Just like Eirika!
たあっ
I'll do it!
いやっ…
I won't lose...!
Me too, me too!
Just like my brother!
I'll keep you safe!
Just you wait.
Innes! I need you...
えへっ
Nice to meet you! Call me Tana. I'm the princess of Frelia.
Hey! It's rude to scare me like that!
My brother always calls me a child, but he's no shining example of maturity...
Flying through the sky on a pegasus makes you feel like you're on top of the world!
Ephraim and Eirika are my very best friends. They're from Renais, did you know?
Is there a way to grow up more quickly? My father and brother need my help!
Protecting you is hard work. I've got to get way stronger!
You got it!
Um...
Here I go!
